  "time_ut": 1658717066,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9\u0db1\u0dd0\u0d9c\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'The President should be given time to build the country'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kotte Vihara party registrar, Rev. Palpola Vipassi Nayak Thero says that the current president Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who has a long political experience, should be given time to build the country.",
        "He also pointed out that everyone should support the President's program to solve the people's problems by freeing the country from the current economic crisis, away from the method of ousting the rulers by holding protests.",
        "Pointing out that the current president has fearlessly accepted the challenge at a time when the country is facing a disaster, he expressed confidence that he will be able to overcome all challenges.",
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe yesterday afternoon (24th) went to Sedawatta, Weheragoda ancient temple and engaged in religious rites.",
        "When the President arrived at the temple, he worshiped King Chaitya, the Bodhi and the Buddha Mandir and engaged in religious rites.",
        "Sedawatta, a temple of historical value, the ancient temple of Weheragoda is a tribute owned by Mrs. Helena Wijewardena and Mr. Don Philip Wijewardena.",
        "Buddhasasana Minister Vidura Wickramanayake, P.M. Mr. Suren Raghavan and Mr. Amari Mandika Wijewardene, Secretary Channa Wickramasinghe and others attended the event."
      ],
